description:
&lt;p&gt;Beyond Compare is a powerful time-saving utility for comparing files and folders on your Windows system.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Use it to manage source code, keep folders in sync, compare program output, and validate copies of your data.&amp;nbsp;
Beyond Compare can create a snapshot of a live directory structure, and compare it against the live copy at a later date.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Beyond Compare helps you analyze differences in detail and carefully reconcile them.&amp;nbsp;

It commands a wide range of file and text operations, as well as script commands for automating tasks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;  compare text files
  &lt;li&gt;  compare folders, zip archives, ftp sites
  &lt;li&gt;  update websites
  &lt;li&gt;  merge code changes
  &lt;li&gt;  compare program output
  &lt;li&gt;  and more
  &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Beyond Compare is a directory compare utility and a file compare utility wrapped in one. Synchronize files between laptop and PC, home and office, etc. Compare directory trees side-by-side with mismatches highlighted. Display text files side-by-side with changes highlighted. Great for merging changes to source code. Supports minor editing, Unicode text files, and Delphi form files. Save favorite sessions for quick access. Built-in FTP and zip support.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;a href=&quot;http://rds.yahoo.com/*http://www.scootersoftware.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Home Page&lt;/a&gt;

Install the app using beycomp.exe, then apply the patch.exe to bc2.exe (in 'beyond compare 2' program files folder) and finally copy the BC2.key to the same folder.
